lution for individuals <strong>seeking relief from leg discomfort and swelling.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHXNK0bxqW_text","label":"ggHXNK0bxqW_text","default":"<p><a href=\"* https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/39222789/\"><u>*https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/39222789/</u></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWaM2WXPMT_text","label":"ggWaM2WXPMT_text","default":"<p><a href=\"** https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1360859224005813\"><u>**https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1360859224005813</u></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9L3EDUCMV_text","label":"gg9L3EDUCMV_text","default":"Loved by Our Customers for a Reason"},{"type":"html","id":"ggL4iNUkg4Z_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggL4iNUkg4Z_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-3236e293-92c7-4b9b-8e31-fb0dae6327de.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGQXnMY5zT_text","label":"ggGQXnMY5zT_text","default":"Loved by Our Customers for a Reason"},{"type":"html","id":"ggihBBrHnWy_text","label":"ggihBBrHnWy_text","default":"<p>People aren’t just using the SmoothSpine™ 3-in-1 Leg Massager - they’re building it into their daily routine.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5A_s7vPft_text","label":"gg5A_s7vPft_text","default":"<p>From the moment they slip it on, they know it’s different. <strong>There’s a rhythm to the way it works.</strong> A calm that sets in. A feeling of lightness that wasn’t there before.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaFHF5sugD_text","label":"ggaFHF5sugD_text","default":"<p>It’s become the thing they reach for after a long day, after hours of standing, or whenever that heavy, swollen feeling returns.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbeYBd0f0Y_text","label":"ggbeYBd0f0Y_text","default":"<p><strong>Once they feel the relief</strong>, they never want to go back.</p>"}],
